name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Goodlato launches our new product, "Ugly Sorbets" on 21st August, 11.30am - 2.30pm at @treatsure pop up at their concept store! Now listen! Approximately 20% of produce or more gets thrown out for cosmetic reasons like weird shapes, odd colors, or blemishes. To fight against unnecessary food waste, we partnered with treatsure to source these "ugly" berries to turn into tasty and refreshing sorbets, in Goodlato style. Because not only are we committed to sustainability, we are also committed to making our products low in calorie and low sugar for a health-driven cause, and this will always be in Goodlato's DNA. See you at the pop up event! Find out more about this event on @treatsure #treatsuresg #goodlato #lowcalorie #sustainable #produce #sustainablesg

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: All good things come to an end and so have Goodlato’s stint at Havelock II, I have decided not to renew the lease despite it being a great place for starting out my business and the amazing customers I’ve came to know during my time there. We will be closed until further notice, but meanwhile we’re still available on Shopee and Lazada! Bear with us, and till next time

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: We’ll be closed on 2nd June (Vesak Day).

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: From May 16th, make your own healthy ice-cream bowl at Goodlato. Options for toppings include Granola, Cocoa Nibs, Mixed Fruits and many more! Made using our low-calorie, low sugar and low fat in-house ice cream, you can beat the heat with this sweet treat without the guilt!For the health conscious peeps, the calories range from ~80kcal for our S bowl (1 base, 1 Topping), ~150kcal for our M bowl (2 bases, 2 Toppings), and ~250kcal for our L bowl 3 bases, 3 Toppings). In celebration of this new menu launch, we’ll be having 50% off our L bowl from 16th to 30th May, in-store only!

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: It’s Monday again. You know what this means! This week, we bring you an announcement - Goodlato will be going to Artbox! (3-5 March). If you see this post, you’re in luck, because you get to enjoy 1-for-1 gelato cups when you visit us at Artbox. Just follow the steps and you’re in! If you think that’s all the goodness we have for you, you’re wrong (did you think so little of us?) - 5 lucky peeps will be able to redeem a free cup from us at Artbox! We’ll choose them next Monday before the next game, so stay tuned for Goodlato’s weekly Monday “pep-me ups”.As always, Goodlato wants to bring you Moo-re of the good times so let’s make this weekly surprise a good thing It’s been a long journey, to all those that have supported and believed in Goodlato so far, this is our way of giving back. Rules1. Repost this post on your stories/insta post and tell us which flavour you’re most excited to try.2. Share and tag us in that post 3. Redeem 1-for-1 Gelato cups at Artbox. * 5 lucky winners will be able to claim a free cup during the eventWhilst stocks last - subject to availability.

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Happy Monday everyone! Let’s play a game. Every Monday we’ll post a question and randomly select 1 lucky winner who answers our question correctly in the comments section. That user will be able to redeem a FREE ice cream scoop in-store. Your choice of flavour. We’re hoping that we can give you something to look forward to, and slot some goodness into your week. Whether it’s mid-week,weekends,after work or during lunch hours, we’d love to spice it up with an ice cream treat for you, as our routines can get boring don’t they? (Ice cream makes everything better) Let’s start with this week’s question. Where are we located? #giveawaysg rulesWinner will be selected on Sunday (the day before the next question gets posted!) once notified, winner will have to redeem their prize within the week, aka before the next winner gets announced! Goodlato wants to bring you Moo-re of the good times so let’s hope and make this a good thing.

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Are you nuts ‘bout Ferrero like us? Well here’s some good news from Goodlato - this hazelnutty flavour is only 490kcal/pint. Indulge in the chocolate wafer and hazelnut bits and satisfy your ferrero cravings, all without the guilt…

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Post appreciation for you guys from yesterday…so thankful for nice customers (friends) like you! Thanks for supporting and believing in Goodlato. We make OUTRAGEOUSLY BOLD, decadent and rich flavoured gelato that are ironically low in calories!

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: The wait is over! We’ve been working really hard on this menu revamp. Goodlato started out 4 months ago, serving y’all artisanal low-calorie gelato that tastes equally decadent. Come December, we have decided to challenge ourselves further by ditching our plain-ole flavours and go all out with blasphemous & outrageous flavour creations. We love challenges, hence, we promised to make them all low-in-calorie, high in protein and do the “impossible”… Ironic ain’t it? But that’s what makes it fun. Come visit us! We promise to fulfil your cheat day dreams. Our scoops go as low as 49kcal/scoop (Normal ice cream is about 200kcal/scoop).- Are you outrageously good or just plain ole boring?

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: It’s day one of our menu revamp. Here’s a new flavour drop for you guys - Strawberry Sakura  keep a lookout for our other new flavours in the coming weeks!

name: Goodlato Handcrafted Low Calorie Gelato
content: Here at Goodlato, we make outrageous and bold flavours into low-calorie goodness. However, we can’t forget the classic flavours too. B is for Boring-I mean, Belgian Chocolate!  Just kidding, we love our Belgian Chocolate too even though it is admittedly “boring”. We still do it well though!
